tblDMIRExtPortfHolding_temp
Staging table receiving raw daily external‑fund holdings extracted from third‑party custodians or administrators. Each record captures external portfolio ISIN, holding date, accounting date, currency, and AUM figures plus audit‑ID metadata. Data lives here temporarily during overnight ETL, then filtered for latest date per fund before loading core look‑through scope tables.

tblDMIRInrPortfHolding_temp
Temporary repository for internally‑managed portfolio holdings sourced from in‑house platforms like Aladdin or SimCorp. Contains GPS code, ISIN, internal audit identifiers, valuation date, currency and assets. Data is truncated and reloaded each cycle, enabling comparison against previous snapshots and feeding internal leg of look‑through calculations into Scope and Monitoring layers.

tblDMIRMonitoringLTWrk
Work‑in‑progress copy of Monitoring Look‑Through table created at process start. Receives merged, cleansed records from internal, external, special and DMC sources, with status flags, audit‑IDs and NAV metrics. Allows complex deletions, insertions and recalculations in isolation; once validated it overwrites production MonitoringLT, ensuring atomic refresh without user disruption or downtime.
